    "media:imagetext": "Land low rates\nwith Alamo.\nNATIONWIDE\n$3399\nDay\nChevy Corsica or similar 4-door midsize\nAdd airport-imposed taxes/fees, if any,\nexcept where prohibited by law.\nWhen you fly TWA, you can land low rates\nwith Alamo. Now, you can reserve a Chevy\nCorsica or similar 4-door midsize car for only\n$33.99 a day nationwide. Great rates are also\navailable on other fine General Motors cars, all\nwith unlimited free mileage nationwide.\nSales tax, optional CDW Waiver Savers™\n($9 per day or less), fuel, additional driver fee\nand other optional items are extra. Rates higher\nfor renters under age 25. Some airports impose\na tax or fee (ranging from 25¢ to 8.5%) that\napplies only if you choose to exit on our shuttle\nbus. A 24-hour advance reservation is required.\nAvailability is limited. Offer good through\nDecember 31, 1991.\nFor reservations call your Professional Travel\nAgent or call Alamo at 1-800-327-9633 and request\nRate Code T8.\nlamo\nRent A Car\nWhere all the miles\nare free\"\nAlamo features fine General Motors\ncars like this Chevy Corsica.\n01 113.209 33429AR",
